Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:06.89,Default,,0,0,1,,你流鼻血了 撞到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.97,0:00:09.09,Default,,0,0,1,,嗯 不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.20,0:00:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我是星十字骑士团「V」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,「消失点」 葛纳尔·李
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.45,0:00:21.25,zhu-2,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,988.8)}Vanishing Point
